+| **SuiteCloud вҖ“ Ventas** *(this service)* | Async | Processes TSL frame, applies business logic, generates XML, persists in Firestore, notifies Distributor Cloud. |
+| **SuiteCloud вҖ“ Consultas** | Sync | Answers real-time queries (prices, stock, customers) from Cloud SQL Multi Local. |
